{
  "snp3.9:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 3.9 ",
  "snp3.9:0.2": "Vāseṭṭhasutta ",
  "snp3.9:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
  "snp3.9:1.2": "ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe. ",
  "snp3.9:1.3": "Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā abhiññātā abhiññātā brāhmaṇamahāsālā icchānaṅgale paṭivasanti, seyyathidaṁ—",
  "snp3.9:1.4": "caṅkī brāhmaṇo, tārukkho brāhmaṇo, pokkharasāti brāhmaṇo, jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo, todeyyo brāhmaṇo, aññe ca abhiññātā abhiññātā brāhmaṇamahāsālā. ",
  "snp3.9:1.5": "Atha kho vāseṭṭhabhāradvājānaṁ māṇavānaṁ jaṅghāvihāraṁ anucaṅkamantānaṁ anuvicarantānaṁ ayamantarākathā udapādi: ",
  "snp3.9:1.6": "“kathaṁ, bho, brāhmaṇo hotī”ti? ",
  "snp3.9:2.1": "Bhāradvājo māṇavo evamāha: ",
  "snp3.9:2.2": "“yato kho, bho, ubhato sujāto hoti mātito ca pitito ca saṁsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, ",
  "snp3.9:2.3": "ettāvatā kho bho brāhmaṇo hotī”ti. ",
  "snp3.9:3.1": "Vāseṭṭho māṇavo evamāha: ",
  "snp3.9:3.2": "“yato kho, bho, sīlavā ca hoti vatasampanno ca, ",
  "snp3.9:3.3": "ettāvatā kho, bho, brāhmaṇo hotī”ti. ",
  "snp3.9:3.4": "Neva kho asakkhi bhāradvājo māṇavo vāseṭṭhaṁ māṇavaṁ saññāpetuṁ, na pana asakkhi vāseṭṭho māṇavo bhāradvājaṁ māṇavaṁ saññāpetuṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:4.1": "Atha kho vāseṭṭho māṇavo bhāradvājaṁ māṇavaṁ āmantesi: ",
  "snp3.9:4.2": "“ayaṁ kho, bho bhāradvāja, samaṇo gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe; ",
  "snp3.9:4.3": "taṁ kho pana bhavantaṁ gotamaṁ evaṁ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato: ",
  "snp3.9:4.4": "‘itipi …pe… buddho bhagavā’ti. ",
  "snp3.9:4.5": "Āyāma, bho bhāradvāja, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkamissāma; upasaṅkamitvā samaṇaṁ gotamaṁ etamatthaṁ pucchissāma. ",
  "snp3.9:4.6": "Yathā no samaṇo gotamo byākarissati tathā naṁ dhāressāmā”ti. ",
  "snp3.9:4.7": "“Evaṁ, bho”ti kho bhāradvājo māṇavo vāseṭṭhassa māṇavassa paccassosi. ",
  "snp3.9:5.1": "Atha kho vāseṭṭhabhāradvājā māṇavā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṁsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṁ sammodiṁsu. ",
  "snp3.9:5.2": "Sammodanīyaṁ kathaṁ sāraṇīyaṁ vītisāretvā ekamantaṁ nisīdiṁsu. ",
  "snp3.9:5.3": "Ekamantaṁ nisinno kho vāseṭṭho māṇavo bhagavantaṁ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "snp3.9:6.1": "“Anuññātapaṭiññātā, ",
  "snp3.9:6.2": "tevijjā mayamasmubho; ",
  "snp3.9:6.3": "Ahaṁ pokkharasātissa, ",
  "snp3.9:6.4": "tārukkhassāyaṁ māṇavo. ",
  "snp3.9:7.1": "Tevijjānaṁ yadakkhātaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:7.2": "Tatra kevalinosmase; ",
  "snp3.9:7.3": "Padakasma veyyākaraṇā, ",
  "snp3.9:7.4": "Jappe ācariyasādisā. ",
  "snp3.9:8.1": "Tesaṁ no jātivādasmiṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:8.2": "vivādo atthi gotama; ",
  "snp3.9:8.3": "Jātiyā brāhmaṇo hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:8.4": "bhāradvājo iti bhāsati; ",
  "snp3.9:8.5": "Ahañca kammunā brūmi, ",
  "snp3.9:8.6": "evaṁ jānāhi cakkhuma. ",
  "snp3.9:9.1": "Te na sakkoma saññāpetuṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:9.2": "aññamaññaṁ mayaṁ ubho; ",
  "snp3.9:9.3": "Bhavantaṁ puṭṭhumāgamhā, ",
  "snp3.9:9.4": "sambuddhaṁ iti vissutaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:10.1": "Candaṁ yathā khayātītaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:10.2": "pecca pañjalikā janā; ",
  "snp3.9:10.3": "Vandamānā namassanti, ",
  "snp3.9:10.4": "evaṁ lokasmi gotamaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:11.1": "Cakkhuṁ loke samuppannaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:11.2": "mayaṁ pucchāma gotamaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:11.3": "Jātiyā brāhmaṇo hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:11.4": "udāhu bhavati kammunā; ",
  "snp3.9:11.5": "Ajānataṁ no pabrūhi, ",
  "snp3.9:11.6": "yathā jānemu brāhmaṇaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.9:12.1": "“Tesaṁ vo ahaṁ byakkhissaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:12.2": "(vāseṭṭhāti bhagavā) ",
  "snp3.9:12.3": "Anupubbaṁ yathātathaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:12.4": "Jātivibhaṅgaṁ pāṇānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:12.5": "Aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:13.1": "Tiṇarukkhepi jānātha, ",
  "snp3.9:13.2": "na cāpi paṭijānare; ",
  "snp3.9:13.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:13.4": "aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:14.1": "Tato kīṭe paṭaṅge ca, ",
  "snp3.9:14.2": "yāva kunthakipillike; ",
  "snp3.9:14.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:14.4": "aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:15.1": "Catuppadepi jānātha, ",
  "snp3.9:15.2": "Khuddake ca mahallake; ",
  "snp3.9:15.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:15.4": "Aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:16.1": "Pādūdarepi jānātha, ",
  "snp3.9:16.2": "Urage dīghapiṭṭhike; ",
  "snp3.9:16.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:16.4": "Aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:17.1": "Tato macchepi jānātha, ",
  "snp3.9:17.2": "Odake vārigocare; ",
  "snp3.9:17.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:17.4": "Aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:18.1": "Tato pakkhīpi jānātha, ",
  "snp3.9:18.2": "Pattayāne vihaṅgame; ",
  "snp3.9:18.3": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ tesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:18.4": "Aññamaññā hi jātiyo. ",
  "snp3.9:19.1": "Yathā etāsu jātīsu, ",
  "snp3.9:19.2": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ puthu; ",
  "snp3.9:19.3": "Evaṁ natthi manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:19.4": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ puthu. ",
  "snp3.9:20.1": "Na kesehi na sīsena, ",
  "snp3.9:20.2": "Na kaṇṇehi na akkhibhi; ",
  "snp3.9:20.3": "Na mukhena na nāsāya, ",
  "snp3.9:20.4": "Na oṭṭhehi bhamūhi vā. ",
  "snp3.9:21.1": "Na gīvāya na aṁsehi, ",
  "snp3.9:21.2": "Na udarena na piṭṭhiyā; ",
  "snp3.9:21.3": "Na soṇiyā na urasā, ",
  "snp3.9:21.4": "Na sambādhe na methune. ",
  "snp3.9:22.1": "Na hatthehi na pādehi, ",
  "snp3.9:22.2": "Nāṅgulīhi nakhehi vā; ",
  "snp3.9:22.3": "Na jaṅghāhi na ūrūhi, ",
  "snp3.9:22.4": "Na vaṇṇena sarena vā; ",
  "snp3.9:22.5": "Liṅgaṁ jātimayaṁ neva, ",
  "snp3.9:22.6": "Yathā aññāsu jātisu. ",
  "snp3.9:23.1": "Paccattañca sarīresu, ",
  "snp3.9:23.2": "Manussesvetaṁ na vijjati; ",
  "snp3.9:23.3": "Vokārañca manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:23.4": "Samaññāya pavuccati. ",
  "snp3.9:24.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:24.2": "Gorakkhaṁ upajīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:24.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:24.4": "Kassako so na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:25.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:25.2": "Puthusippena jīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:25.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:25.4": "Sippiko so na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:26.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:26.2": "Vohāraṁ upajīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:26.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:26.4": "Vāṇijo so na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:27.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:27.2": "Parapessena jīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:27.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:27.4": "Pessiko so na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:28.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:28.2": "Adinnaṁ upajīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:28.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:28.4": "Coro eso na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:29.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:29.2": "Issatthaṁ upajīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:29.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:29.4": "Yodhājīvo na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:30.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:30.2": "Porohiccena jīvati; ",
  "snp3.9:30.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:30.4": "Yājako eso na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:31.1": "Yo hi koci manussesu, ",
  "snp3.9:31.2": "Gāmaṁ raṭṭhañca bhuñjati; ",
  "snp3.9:31.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:31.4": "Rājā eso na brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:32.1": "Na cāhaṁ brāhmaṇaṁ brūmi, ",
  "snp3.9:32.2": "Yonijaṁ mattisambhavaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:32.3": "Bhovādi nāma so hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:32.4": "Sace hoti sakiñcano; ",
  "snp3.9:32.5": "Akiñcanaṁ anādānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:32.6": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:33.1": "Sabbasaṁyojanaṁ chetvā, ",
  "snp3.9:33.2": "Yo ve na paritassati; ",
  "snp3.9:33.3": "Saṅgātigaṁ visaṁyuttaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:33.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:34.1": "Chetvā naddhiṁ varattañca, ",
  "snp3.9:34.2": "Sandānaṁ sahanukkamaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:34.3": "Ukkhittapalighaṁ buddhaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:34.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:35.1": "Akkosaṁ vadhabandhañca, ",
  "snp3.9:35.2": "Aduṭṭho yo titikkhati; ",
  "snp3.9:35.3": "Khantībalaṁ balānīkaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:35.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:36.1": "Akkodhanaṁ vatavantaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:36.2": "Sīlavantaṁ anussadaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:36.3": "Dantaṁ antimasārīraṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:36.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:37.1": "Vāri pokkharapatteva, ",
  "snp3.9:37.2": "Āraggeriva sāsapo; ",
  "snp3.9:37.3": "Yo na limpati kāmesu, ",
  "snp3.9:37.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:38.1": "Yo dukkhassa pajānāti, ",
  "snp3.9:38.2": "Idheva khayamattano; ",
  "snp3.9:38.3": "Pannabhāraṁ visaṁyuttaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:38.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:39.1": "Gambhīrapaññaṁ medhāviṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:39.2": "Maggāmaggassa kovidaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:39.3": "Uttamatthamanuppattaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:39.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:40.1": "Asaṁsaṭṭhaṁ gahaṭṭhehi, ",
  "snp3.9:40.2": "Anāgārehi cūbhayaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:40.3": "Anokasārimappicchaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:40.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:41.1": "Nidhāya daṇḍaṁ bhūtesu, ",
  "snp3.9:41.2": "Tasesu thāvaresu ca; ",
  "snp3.9:41.3": "Yo na hanti na ghāteti, ",
  "snp3.9:41.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:42.1": "Aviruddhaṁ viruddhesu, ",
  "snp3.9:42.2": "Attadaṇḍesu nibbutaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:42.3": "Sādānesu anādānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:42.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:43.1": "Yassa rāgo ca doso ca, ",
  "snp3.9:43.2": "Māno makkho ca pātito; ",
  "snp3.9:43.3": "Sāsaporiva āraggā, ",
  "snp3.9:43.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:44.1": "Akakkasaṁ viññāpaniṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:44.2": "Giraṁ saccamudīraye; ",
  "snp3.9:44.3": "Yāya nābhisaje kañci, ",
  "snp3.9:44.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:45.1": "Yodha dīghaṁ va rassaṁ vā, ",
  "snp3.9:45.2": "Aṇuṁ thūlaṁ subhāsubhaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:45.3": "Loke adinnaṁ nādiyati, ",
  "snp3.9:45.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:46.1": "Āsā yassa na vijjanti, ",
  "snp3.9:46.2": "Asmiṁ loke paramhi ca; ",
  "snp3.9:46.3": "Nirāsāsaṁ visaṁyuttaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:46.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:47.1": "Yassālayā na vijjanti, ",
  "snp3.9:47.2": "Aññāya akathaṅkathī; ",
  "snp3.9:47.3": "Amatogadhamanuppattaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:47.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:48.1": "Yodha puññañca pāpañca, ",
  "snp3.9:48.2": "Ubho saṅgamupaccagā; ",
  "snp3.9:48.3": "Asokaṁ virajaṁ suddhaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:48.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:49.1": "Candaṁva vimalaṁ suddhaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:49.2": "Vippasannamanāvilaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:49.3": "Nandībhavaparikkhīṇaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:49.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:50.1": "Yomaṁ palipathaṁ duggaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:50.2": "Saṁsāraṁ mohamaccagā; ",
  "snp3.9:50.3": "Tiṇṇo pāraṅgato jhāyī, ",
  "snp3.9:50.4": "Anejo akathaṅkathī; ",
  "snp3.9:50.5": "Anupādāya nibbuto, ",
  "snp3.9:50.6": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:51.1": "Yodha kāme pahantvāna, ",
  "snp3.9:51.2": "Anāgāro paribbaje; ",
  "snp3.9:51.3": "Kāmabhavaparikkhīṇaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:51.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:52.1": "Yodha taṇhaṁ pahantvāna, ",
  "snp3.9:52.2": "Anāgāro paribbaje; ",
  "snp3.9:52.3": "Taṇhābhavaparikkhīṇaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:52.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:53.1": "Hitvā mānusakaṁ yogaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:53.2": "Dibbaṁ yogaṁ upaccagā; ",
  "snp3.9:53.3": "Sabbayogavisaṁyuttaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:53.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:54.1": "Hitvā ratiñca aratiṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:54.2": "Sītibhūtaṁ nirūpadhiṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:54.3": "Sabbalokābhibhuṁ vīraṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:54.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:55.1": "Cutiṁ yo vedi sattānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:55.2": "Upapattiñca sabbaso; ",
  "snp3.9:55.3": "Asattaṁ sugataṁ buddhaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:55.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:56.1": "Yassa gatiṁ na jānanti, ",
  "snp3.9:56.2": "Devā gandhabbamānusā; ",
  "snp3.9:56.3": "Khīṇāsavaṁ arahantaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:56.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:57.1": "Yassa pure ca pacchā ca, ",
  "snp3.9:57.2": "Majjhe ca natthi kiñcanaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:57.3": "Akiñcanaṁ anādānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:57.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:58.1": "Usabhaṁ pavaraṁ vīraṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:58.2": "Mahesiṁ vijitāvinaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:58.3": "Anejaṁ nhātakaṁ buddhaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:58.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:59.1": "Pubbenivāsaṁ yo vedi, ",
  "snp3.9:59.2": "Saggāpāyañca passati; ",
  "snp3.9:59.3": "Atho jātikkhayaṁ patto, ",
  "snp3.9:59.4": "Tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:60.1": "Samaññā hesā lokasmiṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:60.2": "Nāmagottaṁ pakappitaṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:60.3": "Sammuccā samudāgataṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:60.4": "Tattha tattha pakappitaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:61.1": "Dīgharattamanusayitaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:61.2": "Diṭṭhigatamajānataṁ; ",
  "snp3.9:61.3": "Ajānantā no pabruvanti, ",
  "snp3.9:61.4": "Jātiyā hoti brāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:62.1": "Na jaccā brāhmaṇo hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:62.2": "Na jaccā hoti abrāhmaṇo; ",
  "snp3.9:62.3": "Kammunā brāhmaṇo hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:62.4": "Kammunā hoti abrāhmaṇo. ",
  "snp3.9:63.1": "Kassako kammunā hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:63.2": "Sippiko hoti kammunā; ",
  "snp3.9:63.3": "Vāṇijo kammunā hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:63.4": "Pessiko hoti kammunā. ",
  "snp3.9:64.1": "Coropi kammunā hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:64.2": "Yodhājīvopi kammunā; ",
  "snp3.9:64.3": "Yājako kammunā hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:64.4": "Rājāpi hoti kammunā. ",
  "snp3.9:65.1": "Evametaṁ yathābhūtaṁ, ",
  "snp3.9:65.2": "Kammaṁ passanti paṇḍitā; ",
  "snp3.9:65.3": "Paṭiccasamuppādadassā, ",
  "snp3.9:65.4": "Kammavipākakovidā. ",
  "snp3.9:66.1": "Kammunā vattati loko, ",
  "snp3.9:66.2": "Kammunā vattati pajā; ",
  "snp3.9:66.3": "Kammanibandhanā sattā, ",
  "snp3.9:66.4": "Rathassāṇīva yāyato. ",
  "snp3.9:67.1": "Tapena brahmacariyena, ",
  "snp3.9:67.2": "Saṁyamena damena ca; ",
  "snp3.9:67.3": "Etena brāhmaṇo hoti, ",
  "snp3.9:67.4": "Etaṁ brāhmaṇamuttamaṁ. ",
  "snp3.9:68.1": "Tīhi vijjāhi sampanno, ",
  "snp3.9:68.2": "santo khīṇapunabbhavo; ",
  "snp3.9:68.3": "Evaṁ vāseṭṭha jānāhi, ",
  "snp3.9:68.4": "brahmā sakko vijānatan”ti. ",
  "snp3.9:69.1": "Evaṁ vutte, vāseṭṭhabhāradvājā māṇavā bhagavantaṁ etadavocuṁ: ",
  "snp3.9:69.2": "“abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama …pe… ",
  "snp3.9:69.3": "upāsake no bhavaṁ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupete saraṇaṁ gate”ti. ",
  "snp3.9:69.4": "Vāseṭṭhasuttaṁ navamaṁ. "
}